description:
God has given us an incredible gift in the power of choice, but it comes with a great responsibility and eternal consequences. How are we using this precious gift? What does the Bible say about the power of choice? How can we yield our physical, mental, and spiritual faculties to Christ’s control so that our thoughts and emotions will be in harmony with His will? Discover the secret to surrendering your will to Christ. Learn how you can experience God’s peace in the midst of conflict.
